column8: It is said that the Saturn V along with its spacecraft contained some 15 million parts. If those parts had been 99.9 percent reliable, there still would have been 15,000 failures. But it had only five failures, all in noncritical parts. Unbelievable quality & performance.
column21:
It is said that the Saturn V along with its spacecraft contained some 15 million parts. If those parts had been 99.9 percent reliable, there still would have been 15,000 failures. But it had only five failures, all in noncritical parts. Unbelievable quality & performance. Admire it, and wear this t shirt with pride.

From weadmire.net.
